---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
// High-Performance B2B Industrial Sub-Homepage for Conveyor Systems
---

<Layout title="Industrial Conveyor Systems & Belts Sri Lanka | E Lanka World">
	
	<main>
		<section class="conveyor-hero-container">
			<picture>
				<img 
					src="/products/industrial-conveyor-systems-sri-lanka.webp" 
					alt="Industrial Packaging Automation Conveyor Lines by E Lanka World International" 
					class="conveyor-hero-img" 
					loading="eager"
					width="1200"
					height="675"
				/>
			</picture>

			<div class="conveyor-hero-overlay">
				<div class="conveyor-lang-stack">
					<span class="sinhala">කාර්මික කන්වෙයර් සිස්ටම් සහ බෙල්ට් වර්ග</span>
					<span class="tamil">இண்டஸ்ட்ரியல் கன்வெயர் சிஸ்டம்ஸ் மற்றும் பெல்ட்கள்</span>
				</div>
				<h1>Industrial Conveyor Systems in Sri Lanka</h1>
				<h2>Premium Automation Infrastructure from E Lanka World International</h2>
				
				<div class="conveyor-cta-group">
					<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="conveyor-whatsapp-btn">Inquire via WhatsApp</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="conveyor-offer-section">
			<div class="conveyor-container">
				<h2 class="conveyor-section-title">Our Specialized Conveyor Categories</h2>
				<p class="conveyor-section-subtitle">Select a category below to explore specific component technical parameters and sizing charts.</p>
				
				<div class="conveyor-grid-hub">
					
					<article class="conveyor-hub-card">
						<div class="conveyor-card-image">
							<img 
								src="/products/conveyor-belts-supplies-sri-lanka.webp" 
								alt="Heavy Duty Spare Conveyor Belts and Replacement Mesh" 
								width="1200"
								height="675"
								loading="lazy"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="conveyor-card-body">
							<h3>Conveyor Belts & Spares</h3>
							<p>Explore replacement parts, premium PVC, PU, heat-resistant configurations, and food-safe modular interlocking plastic mesh belts built to length specifications.</p>
							<a href="/conveyor-accessories" class="conveyor-card-link">View Belt Options &rarr;</a>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="conveyor-hub-card">
						<div class="conveyor-card-image">
							<img 
								src="/products/automated-roller-conveyor-systems.webp" 
								alt="Automated Heavy-Duty Roller Conveyor Assemblies" 
								width="1200"
								height="675"
								loading="lazy"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="conveyor-card-body">
							<h3>Conveyor System Assemblies</h3>
							<p>Heavy-duty driven or gravity stainless steel roller tables, flexible curve loops, and automated speed-controlled transport platforms for production packaging corridors.</p>
							<a href="conveyor-system-assemblies-material-handling-sri-lanka" class="conveyor-card-link">Explore System Types &rarr;</a>
						</div>
					</article>

					<article class="conveyor-hub-card">
						<div class="conveyor-card-image">
							<img 
								src="/products/custom-industrial-packaging-conveyor.webp" 
								alt="Customized Inclined Packaging Conveyor Units" 
								width="1200"
								height="675"
								loading="lazy"
								decoding="async"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="conveyor-card-body">
							<h3>Custom Production Lines</h3>
							<p>Inclined Z-cleat elevators, automated hopper feeding systems, and specialized collection sorting setups perfectly synchronized with filling or sealing modules.</p>
							<a href="custom-production-lines-automated-factory-sri-lanka" class="conveyor-card-link">View Custom Solutions &rarr;</a>
						</div>
					</article>

				</div>

				<div class="conveyor-extra-offer">
					<p>Looking for a tailored factory floor system or custom width configuration?</p>
					<a href="/shop" class="conveyor-secondary-btn">Return to Packaging Shop</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="conveyor-seo-section">
			<div class="conveyor-container">
				<h2 class="conveyor-article-title">Optimize Material Handling Flow with Premium Conveyor Machinery</h2>
				
				<div class="conveyor-article-grid">
					<div class="conveyor-article-text">
						<h3>High Efficiency & Factory Floor Integration</h3>
						<p>
							Integrating a rugged <strong>conveyor system in Sri Lanka</strong> into your packaging line radically minimizes manual dependencies, reduces operational bottlenecks, and protects fragile goods. From continuous bottle lines to heavy cardboard processing setups, our material handling assets handle demanding floor runs with zero drops in operational velocity.
						</p>

						<h3>Dependable Local Stock of Wear-and-Tear Spare Parts</h3>
						<p>
							Conveyor systems run constantly, meaning tracking wear-and-tear items is crucial. At <strong>E Lanka World International</strong>, we back our systems with local spare parts security—including custom PVC tracker bands, high-strength drive pins, replacement rollers, speed controllers, and robust motors right here in Sri Lanka.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="conveyor-article-text">
						<h3>Rugged Structural Engineering & Food-Safe Options</h3>
						<p>
							Our standard systems incorporate corrosion-resistant stainless steel or reinforced aluminum alloy framework to survive industrial operating spaces. For food processing operations, chemical facilities, or bottling lines, we deliver food-safe certified modular chains and specialized cleanable plastic links to fulfill strict sanitary protocols.
						</p>

						<h3>On-Site Fitting & Structural Integration Guidance</h3>
						<p>
							We don't just supply raw hardware components. Our engineering support includes localized configuration mapping, line speed syncing analysis to pair conveyors with inline filling or batch coding equipment, and complete technical assembly verification to maximize long-term machinery return on investment (ROI).
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="conveyor-cta-banner">
					<p>Ready to automate material transitions on your floor? Get accurate component estimates from engineering experts.</p>
					<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="conveyor-primary-btn">Request Setup Estimate</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* --- HERO BLOCK STYLING --- */
	.conveyor-hero-container {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		min-height: 75vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
		background-color: #0f172a;
	}

	.conveyor-hero-img {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		z-index: 1;
		opacity: 0.85;
	}

	.conveyor-hero-overlay {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 15px;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 820px;
		margin: 0 1rem;
		backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
	}

	.conveyor-hero-overlay h1 {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
		color: #001f3f;
		line-height: 1.2;
		margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.conveyor-hero-overlay h2 {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: #2563eb;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}
	
	.conveyor-lang-stack span {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #4b5563;
		margin-bottom: 4px;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.conveyor-whatsapp-btn {
		background: #25D366;
		color: white;
		padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3);
	}
	.conveyor-whatsapp-btn:hover {
		transform: scale(1.03);
		background-color: #20ba5a;
	}

	/* --- PRODUCT GRID HUB STYLING --- */
	.conveyor-offer-section {
		padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
		background-color: #f8fafc;
	}
	
	.conveyor-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.conveyor-section-title {
		font-size: 2.3rem;
		color: #001f3f;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}
	
	.conveyor-section-subtitle {
		color: #64748b;
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.conveyor-grid-hub {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); /* Clean desktop split symmetry */
		gap: 2rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.conveyor-hub-card {
		background: #ffffff;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
		border-top: 5px solid #2563eb;
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.conveyor-hub-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
	}

	.conveyor-card-image {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
		overflow: hidden;
		background-color: #e2e8f0;
	}

	.conveyor-card-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		display: block;
	}

	.conveyor-card-body {
		padding: 1.8rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.conveyor-card-body h3 {
		color: #001f3f;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	
	.conveyor-card-body p {
		color: #475569;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.conveyor-card-link {
		color: #2563eb;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.conveyor-card-link:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
		color: #1d4ed8;
	}

	.conveyor-extra-offer {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		color: #475569;
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	
	.conveyor-secondary-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 1.2rem;
		color: #2563eb;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		border: 2px solid #2563eb;
		padding: 0.7rem 1.8rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
		background: transparent;
	}
	.conveyor-secondary-btn:hover {
		background: #2563eb;
		color: white;
	}

	/* --- SEO TEXT SECTION STYLING --- */
	.conveyor-seo-section {
		padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
		background-color: #ffffff;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #334155;
	}
	
	.conveyor-article-title {
		font-size: 2.1rem;
		color: #001f3f;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.conveyor-article-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.conveyor-article-text h3 {
		color: #2563eb;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.conveyor-article-text p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.conveyor-seo-section strong {
		color: #0f172a;
	}

	/* --- CALL TO ACTION PANEL STYLING --- */
	.conveyor-cta-banner {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		background: #f1f5f9;
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 15px;
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
	}

	.conveyor-cta-banner p {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
		color: #1e293b;
	}

	.conveyor-primary-btn {
		background: #001f3f;
		color: white;
		padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		display: inline-block;
		transition: background 0.2s ease;
	}

	.conveyor-primary-btn:hover {
		background: #2563eb;
	}

	/* --- SCREEN RESPONSIVE LAYOUT BREAKPOINTS --- */
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.conveyor-grid-hub {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 2 Columns across generic tablets */
		}
		.conveyor-article-grid {
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.conveyor-hero-container {
			min-height: 65vh;
		}
		.conveyor-hero-overlay {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
		.conveyor-section-title {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.conveyor-article-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack text modules vertically */
			gap: 1rem;
		}
		.conveyor-article-title {
			font-size: 1.6rem;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}
		.conveyor-cta-banner {
			padding: 2rem 1.2rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.conveyor-grid-hub {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Single column stack output on standard smartphones */
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
		.conveyor-hub-card {
			max-width: 420px;
			margin: 0 auto; /* Keep structural card centered perfectly */
		}
	}
</style>